				<h2 class="articleTitle">Robot Pack Mule to Carry Loads for G.I.s  on the Move</h2>
				<p id="articleDek">Boston Dynamics's Legged Squad Support System is the latest challenge for robotics pioneer Marc Raibert</p>
				<p class="articleInfo">
					
						<span class="byline">
							By  <a href="http://www.scientificamerican.com/author.cfm?id=1324">Larry Greenemeier</a>
						</span>
					&nbsp;|
